  "a tetrahedron sits in a cube with 4 halves around it"
  Ôćĺ Cube = tet + 4*(half tet)
  Ôćĺ Volume: 1 = vol(tet) + 4*(vol(tet)/2) = 3*vol(tet) Ôćĺ vol(tet) = 1/3

